abstract: The Republican Party’s biggest donors are financing a new group to recruit seasoned candidates and protect Senate incumbents from challenges by far-right conservatives and Tea Party enthusiasts.
snippet: The Republican Party’s biggest donors are financing a new group to recruit seasoned candidates and protect Senate incumbents from challenges by far-right conservatives and Tea Party enthusiasts.
lead_paragraph: COUNCIL BLUFFS, Iowa — The biggest donors in the Republican Party are financing a new group to recruit seasoned candidates and protect Senate incumbents from challenges by far-right conservatives and Tea Party enthusiasts who Republican leaders worry could complicate the party’s efforts to win control of the Senate.

abstract: The Islanders  improved to 4-2-1 and closed a five-game trip with a 3-1-1 mark that included a win in overtime on Thursday.
snippet: The Islanders  improved to 4-2-1 and closed a five-game trip with a 3-1-1 mark that included a win in overtime on Thursday.
lead_paragraph: NEWARK — Brad Boyes stuffed in a rebound for a power-play goal at 2 minutes 1 second of overtime, and the resurgent Islanders beat the Devils for the first time in their last five meetings with a taut 5-4 victory Thursday night.

abstract: On mail boats, as little as $45 buys a one-way ticket to the island of your choice. The local tips you get on the way are free.
snippet: On mail boats, as little as $45 buys a one-way ticket to the island of your choice. The local tips you get on the way are free.
lead_paragraph: Waves rolled through the night, pitching the ship from side to side. From the bridge deck, the white sand beaches of the Exumas glowed blue-white under the starlight, and the rising moon spread a thin layer of silver over the sea. A few miles north, toward our destination in Nassau, lightning flickered.

abstract: The action was said to be a message that the board of JPMorgan Chase was a strong watchdog over the nation’s largest bank.
snippet: The action was said to be a message that the board of JPMorgan Chase was a strong watchdog over the nation’s largest bank.
lead_paragraph: Shortly after the markets closed on Tuesday afternoon, an emissary from JPMorgan Chase’s board of directors walked two flights down to the 48th-floor corner office of the bank’s chief executive, Jamie Dimon, to deliver a stark message. The board had voted to slash Mr. Dimon’s annual compensation for 2012 by half.

abstract: Volunteers for Sheriff Joe Arpaio of Maricopa County, Arizona, look a lot like his paid deputies as they keep an eye on schools.
snippet: Volunteers for Sheriff Joe Arpaio of Maricopa County, Arizona, look a lot like his paid deputies as they keep an eye on schools.
lead_paragraph: GILA BEND, Ariz. — Dennis Donowick is a retired truck driver who refused to spend the rest of his days “drinking beer and doing nothing,” as he put it. Four years ago, he packed his guns and his urge “to give back to the community” and joined Sheriff Joe Arpaio’s volunteer posse, a group best known for its supporting role in the sheriff’s immigration raids.
